snippet: The strongest quake felt in the Japanese capital since the aftershocks of a magnitude-9 earthquake and tsunami in March 2011 off the northeastern coast.
abstract: Strong earthquake jolts Tokyo, but there are no initial reports of major damage.
lead_paragraph: The strongest quake felt in the Japanese capital since the aftershocks of a magnitude-9 earthquake and tsunami in March 2011 off the northeastern coast.

headline.main: Tokyo Is Shaken by Strong Quake
